# Rift SDK Wrapper — env vars
#
# The wrapper is essentially stateless. It does not hold any secrets:
# the project API key is read per-request from the X-API-Key header
# and used to instantiate the SDK on the fly. Bearer tokens come from
# the Authorization header. Nothing sensitive needs to live in .env.
#
# Copy this file to .env (or rely on platform-level env vars on the
# host) if you want to override the defaults below.

# Optional. Port the Express server binds to. Defaults to 3000.
# Render / CapRover / Heroku / etc. typically set this automatically;
# leave it unset there.
# PORT=3000
